<Input><Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">CTTCheck:=simplify(subs(b=zeromatrix(Dimension(A)),subs(a=A,b*CharacteristicPolynomialFunction(A))))=subs(b=IdentityMatrix(RowDimension(A)),subs(a=A,b*CharacteristicPolynomialFunction(A)))</Text-field>
