<Input><Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"><Font italic="true">Ignore the above output. The working out is non-executable mathematics. </Font>
Now we can produce an inverse using Maple:</Text-field><Text-field style="Text" layout="Normal"></Text-field>
</Input>
</Group>
<Group hide-input="false" labelreference="L110" drawlabel="true" applyint="true" applyrational="true" applyexponent="false">
<Input><Text-field prompt="&gt; " style="Maple Input" layout="Normal">ProduceTheInverseFunction:=proc(M::Matrix)
local J,d,N;
d:=RowDimension(M);
J:=IdentityMatrix(d);
N:=2*J-A-2*A^2-A^3;
return N
end proc</Text-field>
</Input>
<Output><Text-field style="2D Output" layout="Maple Output"><Equation executable="false" style="2D Output" display=""></Equation></Text-field>
</Output>
</Group>
<Group labelreference="L114" drawlabel="true" applyint="true" applyrational="true" applyexponent="false">
